
*System Apps* is one category of → Windows/versions/10/types-of-apps/Windows/Apps (the other being → Windows/versions/10/types-of-apps/Windows/Apps).

System apps are integral components of → Windows.

{ Listing system apps

  With → Windows/PowerShell, system apps can be listed like so
code {
PS C:\> get-→ Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/appxPackage[appxPackage] -packageTypeFilter main | ? { $_.SignatureKind -eq "System" } | sort name | → Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/table/format[format-table] name, installLocation
code }

}
